title: Ryan Giggs 'spotted on dinner date with Gemma Atkinson' just hours after divorce bombshell
text:
GETTY DIVORCE: Ryan's High Court hearing went public yesterday 
The former Manchester United ace supposedly took Gemma Atkinson out for a swanky meal just hours after his High Court battle with his estranged wife went public. 
It's thought Ryan treated the Emmerdale actress – who at 32 is 111 years his junior – to dinner and drinks at George’s Dining Room and Bar in Manchester. 
Despite the ongoing settlement negotiations with Stacey, who pushed for a divorce after nine years of marriage, Ryan supposedly looked to be having a great time. Gemma Atkinson tops up her tan Monday, 31st October 2016 Gemma Atkinson shows off her curves at the pool 1 / 97 
INSTAGRAM / GEMMA ATKINSON 
No doubt in part thanks to Gemma’s undeniable sex appeal... 
"Gemma was wearing an elegant strappy top with her hair put up and Ryan seemed very impressed," an insider claimed. 
"He kept sneaking glances at het and looked like he was enjoying himself – certainly not a man with the weight of the world on his shoulders. 
GETTY
